HEADWORD: Bicycle
<hw>Bi"cy*cle</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Pref.
<ets>bi-</ets> + <ets>cycle</ets>.]</ety> <def>A light vehicle having
two wheels one behind the other. It has a saddle seat and is propelled
by the rider's feet acting on cranks or levers.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Bicycler</ent>⟦br⟧
